    <h2>Nearly 40,000 people have been rescued worldwide with PLB technology</h2>

    <p>All the major manufacturers of PLBs and other locator devices record survivor stories:</p>
    <p><a href="https://www.acrartex.com/survivors/">Rescue stories from ACR, creators of the ACR ResQLink</a></p>
